---
import CalculatorLayout from '../layouts/CalculatorLayout.astro';

const title = "Privacy Policy - HQ Calculator";
const description = "Privacy Policy for HQ Calculator. Learn how we handle your data, what information we collect, and your rights under GDPR and other privacy regulations.";
---

<CalculatorLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  breadcrumbs={[{ name: 'Privacy Policy', url: '/privacy' }]}
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: March 7, 2026</p>

    <div class="prose max-w-none space-y-8">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          HQ Calculator ("we", "us", or "our") operates the website hqcalculator.com. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you visit our website. We are committed to protecting your privacy and complying with applicable data protection laws, including the European Union General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-3">
          We collect minimal data to improve our service. We do <strong>not</strong> collect personal information such as names, email addresses, or phone numbers unless you voluntarily provide it through our feedback widget.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-text mb-2">2.1 Analytics Data</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-3">
          We use <strong>Cloudflare Web Analytics</strong>, a privacy-first analytics service provided by Cloudflare, Inc. This service:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-text-secondary space-y-1">
          <li>Does <strong>not</strong> use cookies or local storage</li>
          <li>Does <strong>not</strong> track individual users across sites</li>
          <li>Does <strong>not</strong> collect personally identifiable information (PII)</li>
          <li>Collects only aggregate, anonymized data such as page views, referrers, browser type, country, and device type</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mt-3">
          For more information, see <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/web-analytics/" class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare Web Analytics privacy documentation</a>.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-text mt-4 mb-2">2.2 Calculations</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          All calculations are performed entirely in your browser (client-side). No calculation inputs or results are sent to our servers or any third party. Your data stays on your device.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-text mt-4 mb-2">2.3 Feedback Widget</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Our optional feedback widget allows you to rate your experience. Feedback responses are anonymous and do not contain personally identifiable information.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">3. Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          HQ Calculator does <strong>not</strong> set any first-party cookies. We do not use tracking cookies, advertising cookies, or any other type of cookie. Cloudflare Web Analytics operates without cookies. Cloudflare's infrastructure may set essential security cookies (e.g., __cf_bm) to protect against bots and malicious traffic. These are strictly necessary cookies and do not require consent under GDPR.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-3">We use the following third-party services:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-text-secondary space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> (Cloudflare, Inc., USA) — content delivery network (CDN), DNS, DDoS protection, and web analytics. Cloudflare processes traffic data to deliver and protect our website. <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
          <li><strong>Google Fonts</strong> (Google LLC, USA) — web font delivery. When you load our pages, your browser connects to Google's servers to download fonts. Google may log your IP address. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">5. Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-3">
          If you are located in the European Economic Area (EEA), you have the following rights under GDPR:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-text-secondary space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Right of access</strong> — request a copy of data we hold about you</li>
          <li><strong>Right to rectification</strong> — request correction of inaccurate data</li>
          <li><strong>Right to erasure</strong> — request deletion of your data</li>
          <li><strong>Right to restrict processing</strong> — request limitation of data processing</li>
          <li><strong>Right to data portability</strong> — request transfer of your data</li>
          <li><strong>Right to object</strong> — object to processing of your data</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mt-3">
          Since we do not collect personally identifiable information, these rights are largely inapplicable. However, if you believe we hold any personal data about you, please contact us.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">6. Data Retention</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          We do not store personal data. Cloudflare Web Analytics data is aggregated and anonymized, and is retained by Cloudflare in accordance with their data retention policies.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Our website is available to users of all ages. We do not knowingly collect personal information from anyone, including children under 16. Since our calculators operate entirely client-side and we do not collect personal data, no special provisions are required.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. We encourage you to review this page periodically.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">9. Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or wish to exercise your privacy rights, please contact us at:
          <strong>privacy@hqcalculator.com</strong>
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</CalculatorLayout>
